Metadata.Title: The Perfect Doctor Chapter 1
Metadata.Description:
47 is on vacation when he discovers facts that would have made him a medical genius unbelievable -- incompetent and undisciplined lifeguards, incurable patients, and various health hazards.Then 47 made up his mind1. Cure a  fracture patient 2. Cure an ADHD patient3. Cure a narcolepsy patient4. Cure a hyperoxia patient 5. Cure a constipated patient6. Punish all lifeguards for doing nothingGood luck47正在度假的时候发现了令他这个医学天才难以置信的事实——无能而散漫的救生员们、无法医治的病患还有各种健康隐患。
这时47下定了决心
1.治愈一位骨折患者
2.治愈一位多动症病患
3.治愈一位嗜睡症患者
4.治愈一位血氧过高患者
5.治愈一位便秘患者
6.惩罚所有无所事事的救生员
祝你好运

<HCCE>
